textAfterTable: Profile iShares MSCI Mexico Capped UCITS ETF is an open-ended, UCITS compliant exchange traded fund domiciled in Ireland. The investment objective of the Fund is to deliver the performance of the MSCI Mexico Capped Index, less fees and expenses of the Fund. The investment objective is achieved via a direct replication methodology.
